id: VER-rtl-on-parse-failure
kind: verification
name: Parse and backend failures fall back to RTL
status: draft
description: Inspect Planner.decide_with_context: every exception path (JSONDecodeError, general Exception, map composition failure) must return a dict with command=='rtl'. No exception may propagate to the state machine.
verifies: REQ-rtl-on-parse-failure
scope: CMP-planner
method: inspection
executions: 0
latest_outcome: not-run
